589
00:34:39,360 --> 00:34:41,360
[SPEAKER_01] Ma fantazija čovjek.

590
00:34:41,360 --> 00:34:43,360
[SPEAKER_01] Znaš koga čovjek.

591
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:45,360
