602
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:40,360
[SPEAKER_02] Istinsko svojećanje.

603
00:35:40,360 --> 00:35:42,360
[SPEAKER_02] Sa svim drugim.

604
00:35:42,360 --> 00:35:44,360
